-- Japan's Inpex Buys 25% Oil Field Stake in Peru From Local Petrobras Unit
-- Tsuyoshi Inajima
-- 2010-08-06T06:06:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/japan-s-inpex-buys-25-oil-field-stake-in-peru-from-local-petrobras-unit.html

          
          
             Inpex Corp. bought a 25 percent stake
in an onshore oil field in Peru from the local unit of Brazil’s
state-owned Petroleo Brasileiro SA, Japan’s biggest energy
explorer said in a statement today. The value of the acquisition
hasn’t been disclosed.  
